fono: fono (lightweight native voice dictation)
fono:
fono: Fono is a single-binary Rust voice dictation tool: press a hotkey,
fono: speak, and cleaned text is typed at the cursor. Local Whisper +
fono: Qwen models by default, or bring-your-own cloud keys (Groq,
fono: OpenAI, Cerebras, Anthropic, ...). No Electron, no WebKit, no
fono: Python runtime.
fono:
fono: Ships a per-user systemd unit (fono.service) under
fono: /lib/systemd/user/ — enable with: systemctl --user enable --now fono
fono: Homepage: https://github.com/bogdanr/fono
